{"tid":1803711,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"2019 光復香港 時代革命，2020 香港獨立 唯一出路","createTime":"2019-12-30T11:48:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-30T14:42:40.000Z","uid":2719,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"be4334da929d5680e9d52b61d462528c20ac03fe","tid":1803711,"uid":2719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T11:48:23.000Z","msg":"2019 大家做到和勇不分，2020 大家又做唔做到獨民不割呢？<br />\n<br />\n「光復香港，時代革命」，因為呢一句口號，大家力撐咗半年，燃點曬香港人嘅革命之火。2020年，要再突破心理關口，提倡「香港獨立，唯一出路」。如果你覺得累、氣餒，請係心裡面諗起呢八個字撐落去，2020年快到，亦都好快過，咁就抗爭咗半年，快？<br />\n<br />\n黎緊2020年，行動大方向，我希望真係做到「普及黃色經濟圈」同「工會帶領三罷」，希望香港人著重推行呢兩大目標，真係會重創港共政府。<br />\n<br />\n加油。"},{"pid":"9563e1b3878207a6d9a21bb17486ebdc8efb0d2e","tid":1803711,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T12:05:51.000Z","msg":"德國聯署<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">1. deadline 25/12 (成功) </span> <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://bit.ly/2MHkcG1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2MHkcG1&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkZMi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=df19727c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2MHkcG1</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">2. deadline 30/12 (成功) </span> <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://bit.ly/369xL99\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F369xL99&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkZMi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=84ef223d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/369xL99</a></span><br />\n3. <ins>暫時最後一個</ins> deadline 1/1 <span style=\"color: red;\">仲要33000人 </span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">［附教學］ <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1803675\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1803675</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">德國減少對中國和其他非民主國家的依賴</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_09/_01/Petition_98731.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fepetitionen.bundestag.de%2Fpetitionen%2F_2019%2F_09%2F_01%2FPetition_98731.html&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkZMi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=f19fb611\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_09/_01/Petition_98731.html</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">簽完share去tg</span></span>"},{"pid":"c0338e797487ab49a4e4ec9af71f475405483627","tid":1803711,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T14:42:13.000Z","msg":"攬炒=&gt;支爆=&gt;支解=&gt;獨立=&gt;真普選<br />\n<br />\n以上係唯一可行路線圖<br />\n所以根本無必要爭拗口號<br />\n應該集中做實事<br />\n搞黃色經濟圈<br />\n搞海外文宣通過制裁支那法案，加速支爆<br />\n各種行動加速攬炒<br />\n最睇唔起只叫口號唔做野既政棍"},{"pid":"6ccbc8ed4bcc6032de7089dcfdade83dd7723f13","tid":1803711,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T14:42:40.000Z","msg":"拉"}]}